freezeframe-brazilian-butt-lift-100-ml.body:
BRAZILIAN BUTT LIFT 100mL

Say goodbye to pancake butt, now you can enhance your curves in just weeks

The buttocks is an important asset to help shape your back, just as your breasts shape the front of your chest. For varying reasons, and often exacerbated by age, many women experience a flattening of the posterior which affects the contours of the behind and results in an out-of-balance proportion. This lack of proportion can be unappealing in swimsuits and clothes alike, and can be a source of self-consciousness.

Brazilian BUTT LIFT has been developed specifically to re-contour the buttocks and create a more shapely, firmer and lifted posterior which looks perkier and younger.

royal-comfort-mulberry-soft-silk-hypoall.title: Royal Comfort Mulberry Soft Silk Hypoallergenic Pillowcase Twin Pack 51 x 76cm - Champagne Pink
royal-comfort-mulberry-soft-silk-hypoall.body:
Upgrade your and sleep in absolute luxury, night after night, with the Mulberry Silk Pillowcase designed by Royal Comfort!

This pillowcase has been expertly designed, with 100% pure mulberry silk on one side, and premium non-slip material on the other side.

Mulberry Silk contains 18 essential amino acids which are the basic building blocks of protein in the skin and are known for its effectiveness in both the prevention of ageing, and as a natural skin-moisturizing agent.

Silk is the most hypoallergenic of all the natural fibres. It is highly delicate on the skin, and with its natural, temperature-regulating properties, is both cool and soothing to the touch. The hypoallergenic, breathable and chemical-free features of this pillowcase suit all skin types, particularly those with common allergies, and the anti-static properties of the pillowcase ensure that you wake up with healthy, shiny hair every morning.

Features:

  • Brand: Royal Comfort
  • Luxurious silky-smooth texture
  • Anti-static properties ensuring you wake up with healthy, shiny hair
  • Highly delicate on the skin
  • Hypoallergenic, breathable and chemical-free
  • Suitable for common-allergy-sufferers
  • Natural temperature-regulating properties
  • Both durable and breathable
  • Packaged in a white gift-box

Specifications

  • Front Material 100% pure mulberry silk
  • Reverse Material: Non-slip material
  • Dimensions: 51cm x 76cm each pillowcase

Package Contents:

  • 1 x Gift Box (White)
  • 2 x Mulberry Silk Pillowcases
